edin.com%2Fjobs2%2Fview%2F268416708&d=%2FFdMH9g2P1E%2BArNiIPXeJ3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=3eb0b61f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.linkedin.com/jobs2/view/268416708</a><br />\n<br />\nAmazon Web Services is seeking a talented, self-directed marketing manager to contribute to develop and grow the AWS cloud computing businesses through enterprise organizations in the Hong Kong and Taiwan market. This is a unique opportunity to support an exciting, industry-leading technology business.<br />\n<br />\nAs an experienced Marketing Manager, you are responsible for developing, proposing, implementing and measuring highly impactful customer focused marketing and communications plans and campaigns to an identified group of AWS accounts from the Named and Enterprise market segments. The key focus is on drafting and proposing the overall marketing plan to support the market growth locally. In addition to this primary responsibility the Marketing Manager will also support the Executive Engagement (CEO, CIO, CFO, and CMO) Program across AWS customers in the region.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Responsibilities</span>:<br />\n<br />\nPlan, develop, and execute marketing strategies to target technical and business decision makers in enterprise segment throughout HKT<br />\n<br />\nSupport the AWS Executive Engagement program across the region<br />\n<br />\nExecute on the HKT marketing programs and work with the sales team to drive business growth and achieve revenue targets<br />\n<br />\nCreate and successfully drive awareness, adoption, and usage of AWS through innovative, scalable and leveragable platform<br />\n<br />\nCraft and develop compelling messaging and tools focused on customers (solution videos, customer success stories, flyers) for use on the web, at live events and in customer facing programs"},{"pid":"15f231ef3ef8f1a604b5166475b547a885999fcd","tid":99652,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18: